COMMUNITY NEWS: SANTA MONICA; HEAL THE BAY'S EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR RESIGNS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Adi Liberman has resigned as executive director of Heal the Bay to become 
