WORLD CUP USA '94 / QUARTERFINALS; SPOTLIGHT; HEY, DOUBLE FIGURES! 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ELLIOTT ALMOND 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The United States has earned 10 points in its Cup history, including the four 
in this tournament. In 14 games, the Americans are 4-9-1. They have scored 18 
goals, given up 33. ELLIOTT ALMOND 
</P>
