<TEXT>
<P>
 Cecelia Ampuero of Newport Beach was among the first-round winners Wednesday 
in a pre-qualifying tournament for the Toshiba Tennis Classic at Rancho San 
Clemente Tennis and Fitness Club. 
</P>
<P>
