earns a berth in the qualifying tournament for the classic, July 30-31 at La 
Costa Resort & Spa. 
</P>
<P>
 In other matches involving local residents, Lisa Alipaz of Anaheim Hills lost 
to La Costa's Betsy Miringhoff, 6-3, 6-1, and Jennifer Shoudt of Seal Beach 
lost to Bonita's Cammie Foley, 6-0, 6-2. 
