6-5, Colorado; Dan Cross, 6-3, Florida; Tyus Edney, 5-10, UCLA; Shawn Respert, 
6-3, Michigan State; Damon Stoudamire, 5-11, Arizona. Forwards -- Michael 
Finley, 6-6, Wisconsin; Alfred Grigsby, 6-9, California; Alan Henderson, 6-9, 
Indiana; Antonio McDyess, 6-9, Alabama; Lawrence Moten, 6-5, Syracuse; Loe Roe, 
6-7, Massachusetts; Scotty Thurman, 6-6, Arkansas. Centers -- Andrew DeClercq, 
6-10, Florida; Cherokee Parks, 6-11, Duke. MIKE REILLEY 
