</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070794-0323 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 058445 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 7, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 2; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
