 Cuban Crackdown Targets Suspected Profiteers: Cuban authorities are 
investigating hundreds of people suspected of getting rich illegally.The 
authorities are confiscating houses, cars and money as a precaution, state 
prosecutor Juan Escalona said. Escalona, quoted by the state news agency AIN, 
