<P>
 State Housing Grants: Gayle Wilson, wife of Gov. Pete Wilson, trekked to 
Rancho Santa Margarita on Monday and offered $5.6 million in state grants to 
California communities that prove they can streamline construction regulations 
by waiving building fees and speeding up the construction permit process. 
</P>
<P>
